{"tid":619863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"母子戀禁室培慾爆煲　女被打內地男友涉偷錢被捕","createTime":"2018-04-07T05:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T05:35:22.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe9c72881ac367c1aa73bd24e6c2d4c5ea0f510","tid":619863,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:28:03.000Z","msg":"母子戀禁室培慾爆煲　女被打男涉偷錢被捕<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙一對母子戀情侶鬧分手反鎖屋內爭執，驚動警方到場。現場為瓊東街8號嘉鋒臺5座一單位，年約40歲女住客結識一名年僅20歲的內地男友，對方早前來港探望，今早10時許，男方突提出分手，並要求立即離開。惟女子不答充，雙方發生爭執，男友突擬爬窗離去，女子趨前制止，糾纏間遭人追打，她退回房間及報案。 <br />\n<br />\n警員接報聯同消防趕至，進入單位調查，初步相信是情侶糾紛，女子又報稱銀包內300元現金失去，內地男友涉嫌偷竊被帶署扣查，而女子則由救護車送院治理。"},{"pid":"80691f0a6fddd689ba80c5347b026e6930aa77af","tid":619863,"uid":153778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/133325_dbc6d360094da7bb47263618f98ca226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F133325_dbc6d360094da7bb47263618f98ca226.jpg&h=29fb2706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果個女人係咁樣，我都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5495fd3fd228f97c41183504f6e21d4f2f263fe9","tid":619863,"uid":33796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba69496922d54144ccf97357daba751c72e9afe8","tid":619863,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05: